reviewText: The Go-go's, when I hear that name I remember an era that was fun and over the top, music was simple and the styles were eye catching (to say the least), but none the less, this early performance is a look at their raw talent that would catapult them into pop culture history, their uptempo songs to this day will still get you feet tapping, if you want to see a classic rare performance that is sure to please any fan, then this is definately for you.
